         <abstract id="aspace_bfd9391186df79d21568baa9b1efe19d">The collection consists of reports, speeches, and printed material relating to the history of Lesotho and the current political, economic, and social conditions. Photographs are also included.</abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_7a9699342d6e485f77a9c66bb3c11bdb">
            <language> The material is in English and Sotho.</language>
         </langmaterial>
    
